title: A Look Back at MaryGirl Moody
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: This is so great I love the Halloween livestream😂
Brought a smile to my face. You are a light in this world. Thank you.
Looking forward to the next Halloween stream and more back flips lol
I love your  channel thanks for all the good moments you gave me;!

Your first reviews were "closeted" lol! I loved this gift you made for us. 
Think I found you a little over a year and 1/2 ago during a big bout with kidney stones. I remember taking something to help me sleep (and I usually don't take anything, not even Tylenol) and then being BEYOND mortified the next day... saw that I had binge watched a bunch of your videos and sleep-commented, critiquing the pronunciation of Taissa Farmiga's name on several of them! I was sleep bitching!
